snippet.title: Stella Fantasy : The Day of The Meteors💫
snippet.description:
On the day countless meteors covered the night sky…🌙

‘Esterium’💠, an element with mysterious powers, falls into the hands of mankind. 

Will it be a new blessing for mankind or a trigger for an inevitable doom?

Stella Fantasy – the story of its origin.
